<HL>
   Business Brief -- Potlatch Corp.:
   Second-Quarter Profit Fell
   64% on a 1.5% Sales Decline
</HL>
<DATE>
07/15/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
<CO>
   PCH
</CO>
